    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
